        <Parent_String>kilns by form [300006395], kilns [300022798], heating equipment [300163292], cooling, heating and humidifying equipment [300163291], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
